@startuml
title ShopSmart Order Lifecycle State Machine

[*] --> PENDING : Customer Checks Out Cart
note right of PENDING : Requires Payment capture

PENDING --> CONFIRMED : Payment Gateway Appoved
PENDING --> CANCELLED : Payment Timeout / Failed

CONFIRMED --> PROCESSING : Merchant Acknowledges
PROCESSING --> SHIPPED : Product Package Dispatched
SHIPPED --> DELIVERED : Marked Received by Carrier API

CONFIRMED --> CANCELLED : Admin Rejects Order
PROCESSING --> CANCELLED : Out of Stock Unresolvable Risk

DELIVERED --> REFUNDED : Customer return initiated and approved
DELIVERED --> [*] : Completion Flow
CANCELLED --> [*] : Termination Flow
REFUNDED --> [*]

@enduml
